## Installation

```bash
$ pip install covidbr -U
```

## Examples

### Get data from cities

```py
import covidbr as cb
cb.show_console(True)

place = 'Juazeiro BA'
data_pet = cb.city(place)

```

### getting the light data 

```py
dataset = data_city.dados
dados
```

